        <h1>Remedies for frizzyhair</h1>
        <h2>Vitamin E and coconut oil </h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Vitamin E is rich in antioxidants and can fix hair damage, coconut oil can condition your hair.
            Oxidative stress and free radicals often cause cells in the scalp to break down, causing scalp damage and interruptions in hair growth. 
            Vitamin E for hair is heavy on antioxidant content that stops hair weakening, reduces stress and maintains hair health.
        </p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Mix 20 drops of vitamin E oil with 3 to 5 tablespoons of coconut oil.</li>
            <li>You can use any coconut oil available in the market and for vitamin E, use capsules that can be punctured.</li> 
            <li>Apply this on your hair at least 40 minutes before washing. </li>
            <li>For better results, leave it on overnight and wash it off with a gentle shampoo.</li>
        </ol>
            </div>
