        <h2>Egg and Olive oil</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Eggs have a high protein content and have the ability to smoothen frizzy hair.
             Moreover, it has moisturising properties which will be beneficial to tame the frizz.</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Whisk one egg with olive oil (take according to the length of your hair), until the mixture is well combined.</li> 
            <li>Apply this to your hair.</li>
            <li>Ensure that the length of your hair is covered with this powerful hair mask.</li> 
            <li>Keep it on for 40 minutes to an hour before washing it off with a gentle shampoo.</li>
        </ol>   
            </div>
