        <h2>Aloe vera and almond oil </h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Aloe vera is known for its moisturising properties while almond oil is rich in vitamin E which helps fight off damage.</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Mix a quarter cup of aloe vera gel with a quarter cup of almond oil.</li> 
            <li>Apply this to the scalp and the length of your hair. </li>
            <li> Massage this mixture in your hair and leave it on for an hour.</li>
            <li>For best results, let it rest in your hair overnight.</li>
            <li></li>Wash off with a gentle shampoo.</li>
        </ol>
