        <h2>Coconut milk</h2>
            <div class="xyz">
                <div class="pqr">
            <p>Coconut milk can help repair hair damage and smoothen your hair due to its high protein content.
                 It helps nourish your hair and make them soft.</p>
            <p>How to apply this?</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Lightly heat the coconut milk.</li>
                <li>After cooling, apply it evenly to your scalp and hair. Let it penetrate deeply into the scalp.</li>
                <li>Cover your head with a warm cloth or towel.</li>
                <li>Wash your hair after half an hour.</li>
                <li>Repeat at least twice a week for best results.</li>
            </ol>
